  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "Currently we publish all `@truffle` libraries w/ only a `package.json`. This is because there is only a `package.json` in those pkg directories (no `shrinkwrap`). See #2555 for the possible security issues with this current setup.\r\n\r\nWe should generate a `package-lock` & then generate a `shrinkwrap` for our library users and proceed with publishing our `@truffle` modules with a `shrinkwrap`.",
